[Labor productivity losses attributable to premature deaths due to traffic 
injuries between 2002 and 2012].

[Article in Spanish]

Cubí-Mollá P(1), Peña-Longobardo LM(2), Casal B(3), Rivera B(3), Oliva-Moreno 
